data.description: Welcome to your dream home with NO MUD TAX!Enjoy the convenience of a close walk to school and the neighborhood pool.This gem boasts an open floor plan adorned with soaring ceilings and elegant wood-look tile.NEW carpet and fresh paint throughout!Revel in the abundance of space,featuring 4 bedrooms and a versatile media room for all your entertainment needs.The living room is a masterpiece with stunning stone work,seamlessly connecting to an open kitchen that overlooks the entire space,creating the perfect hub for family gatherings.Unwind in the expansive bedrooms,each equipped with huge walk-in closets for maximum storage.The allure extends outdoors with a vast back patio,inviting you to savor the joy of BBQs and relaxation.Experience tranquility on the quiet front patio sipping your morning coffee.This home is situated in the renowned CCISD school district.Don't miss the chance to own this blend of sophistication and comfort-schedule your viewing today!Ask about negotiable items!
